item.description: Install and Run GINsim Availability and Requirements GINsim 3.0 is freely available without guarantees. Please contact us for training, other support or dedicated development. The GINsim website (https://ginsim.github.io)[https://ginsim.github.io] provides the latest official version of the software, documentation, as well as a model library.
